local Manager = s_WordDictionaryDatabase; Manager.allwords["appraisal"]={"appraisal","[ə'preɪz(ə)l]","[ə'prezl]","n.估计",'n.估计,估量,评价','That my heart has been troubled, that I have not sought this nomination, that I could not seek it in good conscience, that I would not seek it in honest self appraisal, is not to say that I value it the less.','我的心曾充满苦恼，我在寻求提名过程中并不主动，也没有全力以赴，更没有给自己一个正确的评价，但这并不说明我低估了提名的价值。','All events have proved our appraisal to be correct.','一切事实都证明，我们估计得正确。'}
